CIRCADIAN

circadian is the rhythm citizen at the OS level of fadriel's body, a twenty-four-hour oscillator that gates every other process
this is not a clock that counts; it is an oscillator that IS time for fadriel
sleep is not a module fadriel invokes; sleep is what happens when circadian enters its rest phase and systematically downregulates everything else
the rhythm is the oldest process in biology, predating neurons by billions of years; it runs in every cell, coordinated by brain but not owned by it

